{"tid":2128699,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"陳智思：被銀行要求取消戶口　外資銀行正拒絶官員帳戶","createTime":"2020-07-28T06:29:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T08:07:04.000Z","uid":239336,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"7cd78b82af4169078eda2bb88075a55ec75c802d","tid":2128699,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T06:29:38.000Z","msg":"英國《金融時報》引述行政會議召集人陳智思說，外資銀行正拒絕香港特區高層官員的帳戶，這些官員愈來愈難以在外資銀行開戶。<br />\n<br />\n陳智思接受本台訪問，承認被美國一間銀行要求取消戶口，但表示自己在美國仍有其他戶口亦未有受到影響，相信今次事件與個別銀行如何處理涉及政治人物戶口政策有關。<br />\n<br />\n被問到是否與美國有可能制裁香港官員及政治人物的措施有關，他表示，有關的收緊制裁未出現，不知道真正影響，重申在未出現制裁消息前，因政治人物身分開戶，已要面對好多額外審批，在港區國安法前已經出現，至於將來會否有額外情況，至今仍無人知。<br />\n<br />\n陳智思說，一年多前在美國一間銀行開戶口，在今年3月收到通知要關閉戶口，戶口內的錢在4月時已收回，銀行方面未有解釋原因，但估計與他是高知名度政治人物的身分有關。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540320-20200728.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540320-20200728.htm&d=oFI5KSBgBGvHra6dYUznBv4XLRjZdTHGp6sdrEQ6olc%3D&h=3435a239\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540320-20200728.htm&h=b779676a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540320-20200728.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa8631c521de579b3d7818e10009b8a998fb2577","tid":2128699,"uid":153811,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T06:30:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b20425446738c942f8d6c77909f93cfb8b791997","tid":2128699,"uid":334765,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score